Nosipho.Mkhize THE inaugural Essence Festival Durban will begin in eThekwini on 8 to 13 November. The conference aims to promote radical economic transformation agenda and will include revered business personalities, including Phuthi Mahanyele, Thina Maziya, Busi Skenjana, Ipileng Mkhari, Mzwanele Manyi, Kenyan business woman Tabitha M. Karanja, Bethlemen Tilahun Alemui from Ethiopia and more. 24.com encourages commentary submitted via MyNews24. Contributions of 200 words or more will be considered for publication.